bannerContent: Now sell on one of the best marketplace platforms to get maximum sales and visibility. No need to involve in the hassle to find a new customer for your product. This marketplace will resolve all your issues. So waiting for what hurry up!

sellersData.companyDescription: Marketplace Multi-Vendor Module for Magento 2: Multi-Vendor Marketplace Extension converts your existing Magento 2 Store into a complete online shopping mall marketplace with multiple sellers. Using this extension, the suppliers/sellers can manage the inventory, shipment, Seller Profile page, Seller Collection page. The supplier/seller can add multiple types of products - Simple, Configurable, Virtual & Downloadable. This extension is supported by many shipping & payment add-ons including FedEx, USPS, DHL, PayPal, Stripe, Aramex.You can check out all the Shipping Modules and Payment Extensions. Also, Multi-Vendor Marketplace Mobile App (iOS, Andriod) is also available - Magento 2 Multi-Vendor Mobile App
